OL,3,C'No longer trapped': Woman says rapist
OL,4,Cbeing jailed means she can 'live again'
OL,6,FA Sikh woman who was violently raped
OL,7,Fin a racist attack has said seeing her
OL,8,Fattacker plead guilty means she is "no
OL,9,Flonger trapped" and can finally "live
OL,10,Flife again" .
OL,12,FThe woman, who cannot be named, was
OL,13,Fattacked after being followed back to
OL,14,Fher home in Walsall by a man who
OL,15,Fwrongly believed she was Muslim.
OL,17,FJohn Ashby, who's 32 and of no fixed
OL,18,Fabode, attacked the victim after
OL,19,Ftravelling on the same bus as her. He
OL,20,Ffollowed her home and entered while
OL,21,Fshe was upstairs.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
