SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777119066
OL,3,C'No longer trapped': Woman says rapist
OL,4,Cbeing jailed means she can 'live again'
OL,6,FToday, he was sentenced to life in
OL,7,Fprison with a minimum of 14 years at
OL,8,FBirmingham Crown Court.
OL,10,FDuring the hearing, a victim impact
OL,11,Fstatement was read out on the woman's
OL,12,Fbehalf.
OL,14,FIt said: "What happened to me has
OL,15,Fchanged every part of my life.
OL,17,F"Before life was great, I was happy
OL,18,Fand doing well in my job, I was
OL,19,Fenjoying life and would go out with
OL,20,Ffriends and family.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777119066
OL,3,C'No longer trapped': Woman says rapist
OL,4,Cbeing jailed means she can 'live again'
OL,6,F"I had plans for the future, me and my
OL,7,Fpartner were going to get married in
OL,8,FIndia in January.
OL,10,F"Now my life has drastically changed.
OL,11,FThat version of my life has been
OL,12,Fstripped away by a complete stranger."
OL,14,FThe court heard how Ashby had followed
OL,15,Fthe woman and broke into her home,
OL,16,Fbefore violently raping her.
OL,18,FCCTV images show convicted rapist John
OL,19,FAshby on a bus, before following his
OL,20,Fvictim to her home in Walsall before
OL,21,Fthe attack.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777119066
OL,3,C'No longer trapped': Woman says rapist
OL,4,Cbeing jailed means she can 'live again'
OL,6,F'I feel lost'
OL,8,FThe statement continued: "I feel lost.
OL,9,FI feel like my sense of safety has
OL,10,Fbeen taken from me.
OL,12,F"Since the incident I have felt
OL,13,Fextremely isolated and vulnerable.
OL,15,F"I could not go back to the place I
OL,16,Fcalled my home, it was my safe place.
OL,18,F"This was the place I shared many
OL,19,Fhappy memories with my partner, this
OL,20,Fwas ripped away after what the
OL,21,Fstranger did.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777119066
OL,3,C'No longer trapped': Woman says rapist
OL,4,Cbeing jailed means she can 'live again'
OL,6,F"I felt violated within my own home
OL,7,Fand I knew I would never feel safe
OL,8,Fagain in the place that was my home."
OL,10,FFollowing the incident, the woman
OL,11,Fmoved house, but said she still feels
OL,12,Fscared in her new home. She also said
OL,13,Fshe had to leave her job as she was
OL,14,Funable to keep working, which put a
OL,15,Ffinancial strain on herself and her
OL,16,Fpartner.
OL,18,F'I am no longer trapped'
OL,26,@pD@eO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777119066
OL,3,C'No longer trapped': Woman says rapist
OL,4,Cbeing jailed means she can 'live again'
OL,6,FThe survivor made the decision to
OL,7,Fattend court in person and did not sit
OL,8,Fbehind a screen.
OL,10,FShe said: "I would no longer let this
OL,11,Fperson and this incident control my
OL,12,Flife. I wanted to face the person who
OL,13,Fhas done this to me, see him eye to
OL,14,Feye.
OL,16,F"Hearing him plead guilty made me feel
OL,17,Femotional, I am now no longer trapped.
OL,19,F"Knowing he can no longer hurt me - I
OL,20,Fcan begin to live my life again.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777119066
OL,3,C'No longer trapped': Woman says rapist
OL,4,Cbeing jailed means she can 'live again'
OL,6,F"Now I can look forward to the future
OL,7,Fwith my partner. I hope we can get
OL,8,Fmarried and I can return to work.
OL,10,F"I refuse to let this define me and
OL,11,Fstop me living my life to the fullest."
OL,13,F'Fear in the community'
OL,15,FThe survivor has been supported by the
OL,16,Fcharity Sikh Women's Aid.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777119066
OL,3,C'No longer trapped': Woman says rapist
OL,4,Cbeing jailed means she can 'live again'
OL,6,FSukhvinder Kaur, who works for the
OL,7,Fcharity, told ITV News: "This woman
OL,8,Fthroughout that attack had thought
OL,9,F'I'm going to be killed, this is it
OL,10,Ffor me.'
OL,12,F"That's what hatred in the midst of an
OL,13,Fattack does. It was almost like she
OL,14,Fwas deserving of this attack because
OL,15,Fof her race and religion.
OL,17,F"It does strike fear into the hearts
OL,18,Fof not just that woman, but a
OL,19,Fcommunity."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777119066
OL,3,C'No longer trapped': Woman says rapist
OL,4,Cbeing jailed means she can 'live again'
OL,6,FSpeaking to the woman, Judge Mr
OL,7,FJustice Pepperall said: "I have
OL,8,Fnothing but admiration for your
OL,9,Fbravery.
OL,11,F"Preparing yourself mentally to give
OL,12,Fevidence, coming into court to see
OL,13,Fyour abuser as he entered his guilty
OL,14,Fpleas.
OL,16,F"I am so sorry for the impact this has
OL,17,Fhad on you. I hope with time, love and
OL,18,Fsupport you are able to rebuild your
OL,19,Flives."
OL,21,F'Dangerous man'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777119066
OL,3,C'No longer trapped': Woman says rapist
OL,4,Cbeing jailed means she can 'live again'
OL,6,FThe judge continued: "You are a very
OL,7,Fdangerous man and you pose a
OL,8,Fsignificant risk to women of harm and
OL,9,Ffurther sexual offences.
OL,11,F"You pose an extreme level of danger
OL,12,Fto the public, and particularly women.
OL,13,FThere is no reliable way of estimating
OL,14,Fhow long you will remain a danger.
OL,16,F"Your victim has waited months and
OL,17,Fprepared for trial. Your late guilty
OL,18,Fplea did not spare her."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
