OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1777119066
OL,3,C'No longer trapped': Woman says rapist
OL,4,Cbeing jailed means she can 'live again'
OL,6,FAshby initially denied all charges,
OL,7,Fbut later changed his pleas and
OL,8,Fadmitted rape, intentional
OL,9,Fstrangulation, robbery as he stole
OL,10,Fjewellery and a mobile phone as he
OL,11,Fleft the house, and religiously-
OL,12,Faggravated assault.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/11
